---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title='Repair & Insurance Work in Middlesex & the Home Counties | Hancock' description='Professional repair & insurance work across Middlesex and the Home Counties. Fixed-price quotes, City & Guilds certified, no subcontractors.' activePage='services'>
<section style="position:relative;height:420px;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;">
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background-image:url('/uploads/Hancock-plastering-and-painting%20(2).webp');background-size:cover;background-position:center 25%;"></div>
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(15,23,42,0.9) 0%,rgba(15,23,42,0.45) 60%,rgba(15,23,42,0.15) 100%);"></div>
  <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px 56px;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;">
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);margin:0 0 12px;"><a href="/" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Home</a> / <a href="/services" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Services</a> / Repair &amp; Insurance Work</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(36px,5vw,56px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 14px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1.05;">Repair &amp; Insurance Work</h1>
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:18px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);margin:0;max-width:500px;line-height:1.5;">Plaster and paint damage from water, subsidence, or accidental damage. Documented for insurers.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:72px 24px;background:#ffffff;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">What we cover</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,34px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 24px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">Damage that needs more than a patch and a coat of paint.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 20px;">Burst pipes, roof leaks, subsidence movement, and storm damage all leave plaster and paint in a state that can't be cosmetically treated. The damaged material needs removing, the cause needs addressing, and the wall or ceiling needs replastering and redecorating.</p>
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 20px;">We provide detailed scope of works documentation suitable for insurance claims. We'll describe what was damaged, what was removed, what was applied, and why — in plain language that adjusters and loss assessors understand.</p>
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">Fixed-price quotes provided before work starts, which is what your insurer will need to approve the claim.</p>
    <div style="margin-top:32px;padding:24px;background:#FFF8ED;border:1px solid #FDE68A;border-radius:8px;">
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#92400E;margin:0;line-height:1.7;"><strong>Note:</strong> We work directly with homeowners on insurance claims. We don't work with loss adjusters directly — all engagement is via the homeowner. Quote the damage to us, we'll provide the documentation you need to submit the claim.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:64px 24px;background:#0F172A;">
  <div style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;">
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(26px,4vw,40px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 16px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;">Get a repair quote.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);margin:0 0 36px;">Fixed price with full documentation for insurance.</p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:14px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/contact" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:#0C7BA8;color:#ffffff;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;padding:15px 30px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;">Get a Free Quote</a>
      <a href="tel:07734903439" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);color:#ffffff;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:500;padding:15px 30px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);">07734 903439</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
